description: The Department of National Defence (DND) has a requirement for the supply, delivery, installation and training in Dundurn, Saskatchewan of a Vertical Tillage Disc (VTD) attachment. The VTD will be used to maintain a fireguard around and within the training area  to roll over and expose the soil. The bidder must be able to supply 1 new VTD attachment within the requested timeframe. This is a tender for the supply of an item of equipment. The bidder must be able to deliver the VTD attachment to the location specified on the quoted timeframe.
